						<p>Slab standing in <hi rend="italic">Teṅka-bayalu.</hi></p>						

						<p>Circa 15th century.</p>						

						<p>This badly damaged record in characters of about the 15th-16th century registers gifts of land gold Narasiṁha. It refers to a certain dēvarasa. All other details are lost.</p>						

